tip.text: Very yummy & value for money. Set lunch starts at €9.70 inclusive of salad and coffee or tea.The beef brisket (replaced pork neck) was very tender and delicious.

Quite enjoyed the Earl Grey Choco. A nice, light dessert with nice hints of earl grey, chocolate and sliced banana in the middle.
